Troubleshoot, revise, rework, reorganize, optimize, add or remove any logic necessary for fixing a issue where the blocks' state is saved to local storage and can be exported to or imported from a JSON file.The issue reported is that the colors set by the user are not saved in the JSON file. When the user loads the diagram, the default color of the initial blocks which is lightgreen, and the added blocks are set to 'transparent' instead of the colors the user defined when the diagram was saved.